- Response time is a critical metric for evaluating the efficiency of stakeholders in reacting to alerts.; 
- The average response time is a useful indicator of how quickly stakeholders respond to alerts on average.; 
- Locations with shorter average response times may indicate more effective communication or more efficient processes.

sql:
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_measurements
FROM measurements
WHERE location_id = (SELECT location_id FROM locations WHERE location_name = 'US National');
